                  <persName corresp="PRS0000" instant="false" full="yes">According to the colophon and Additio 1, däğğazmač Ḍäḥayä Lǝda is the donor. In the colophon, his relatives are also mentioned: his wife Wälättä Giyorgis, his father Gäbrä ʾAmlak (s. also Additio 2), his mother Wälättä Täklä Haymanot and priest Gäbrä Giyorgis. The name of Ḍäḥayä Lǝda, a few times together with his wife, is present in the supplication formulas throughout the Ms.&#xD;
